content: I think I'll make some quiches with ham and cheese, and some with spinach and feta. That way, I'll have a good mix of options for my friends. By the way, speaking of friends, I was just thinking about our weekend trip to the beach with Rachel and Mike. We had such a great time playing games and watching the sunset at that cozy accommodation. I'm so glad we got to spend two nights together, it was really nice to unwind.
